        //
        // Dev scenarios use a two-level structure:
        //   Outer (sequence): ⚡ Stop: All Dev → <Scenario> (start)
        //   Inner (parallel): all leaf terminals launch simultaneously
        //
        // When switching scenarios, the stop task kills dev ports
        // (3000, 4000) and Tauri/Capacitor processes. Because leaf
        // tasks have close: true, their terminals vanish automatically,
        // giving you a clean split view for the new scenario.
        // ============================================================

        // Inner parallel start tasks (not meant to be run directly)
        {
            "label": "▶ Web: Dev (start)",
